<div class="about">
	<div class="index">
		<div class="text">
			<h1>Welcome to Theriodex!</h1>

			<figure style="float: left; margin: 0 15px 10px 0;">
				<img src="logo.webp" width="120">
				<figcaption>Vappy says hello!</figcaption>
			</figure>

			<p>Hello and welcome to <b>Theriodex</b>! Theriodex is an open-source and ad-free Pokédex! Its aim is to provide you with the most important information you need at a glance! This site is still a work-in-progress; therefore, don't hesitate to contact us if you have any ideas for improvement!</p>

			<p>There are plenty of things to do here! You can try your luck at the <a href="/game">Who's That Pokémon?</a> guessing game either by doing the default endless mode or by doing the daily Pokémon challenge! You can also be shown a <a href="/random">random Pokémon</a>, search for Pokémon or moves or simply browse the database for – for example – all Pokémon of a particular type!</p>

			<p>Don't like the font, theme or cursor? To into the <a href="/settings">Settings</a> to change them to your liking! You can also unlock more customisation options by playing the game and reaching a certain score!</p>
		</div>

		<div class="random-index-pokemon-container">
			<div class="random-index-pokemon">
				<div>
					<h2>Do you know <%= name %>?</h2>
					<div class="type-container">
					<% types.each do |type| %>
						<a style="text-decoration: none;" href="/show/pokemon/type/<%= type.first.to_s %>?lang=<%= lang %>" aria-label="Pokémon type <%= type.first.to_s %>">
						<div id="<%= type.first.to_s %>" class="move-type-card move-type-card-name rounded"></div>
						</a>
					<% end %>
					</div>
				</div>
				<br>

				<div class="index-sprites-text">
					<div class="sprites">
						<%= image_tag sprite, alt: "#{name} front sprite" %>
					</div>

					<div class="flavour-index">
						<p><%= flavour_text %></p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div>
					<a class="a-btn-1" href="/show/pokemon/<%= name %>">Learn more!</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
